snippet: Epiphanny Prince had 25 points, 7 rebounds and 5 assists, and the Liberty beat the Connecticut Sun, 74-64, at Madison Square Garden.
abstract: New York Liberty defeats Connecticut Sun, 74-64, to secure top overall seed in WNBA playoffs for first time in franchise history; other basketball news noted.
lead_paragraph: Epiphanny Prince had 25 points, 7 rebounds and 5 assists, and the Liberty beat the Connecticut Sun, 74-64, at Madison Square Garden.

headline.main: Liberty Clinch Top Seed in W.N.B.A. Playoffs
